  "decision_conditions": [
    "Condition : 1 - The advertisment display hereby approved shall be for a period of 5 years",
    "Condition : 2 - The intensity of the illumination of the sign shall not exceed 300cd/m2 at any time, as those terms are defined by the Road Vehicles Lighting Regulations 1989 (as amended) or any successor Regulations.",
    "Condition : 3 - The sign shall have static illumination and shall not display any moving, or apparently moving, images.",
    "Condition : 4 - The signs shall be fitted with a light intensity monitoring sensor to ensure the illuminance intensity is dimmable to take account of ambient light conditions and comply with the maximum recommended lighting intensity.",
    "Condition : 5 - In the event of any display defect, malfunction or error the signs shall each be turned off until rectified.",
    "Condition : 6 - The construction of the sign shall not block or impede the flow of the carriageway or footway of the A4 Great West Road at any time."
